Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:09.60,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}相互碰撞的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:12.27,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使如此  我也想拥有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:14.53,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}巨大的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:19.20,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就在这里  从此起步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:22.08,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我明白的  不净是快乐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:25.16,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这是在考验我们吧  我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:28.08,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因为  这份痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:30.12,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}会让我们通往未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:34.05,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大家齐心协力能让自己变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:35.21,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:38.63,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不断的变化  We'll be star!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:43.64,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如果能为自己所喜欢的事加油的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:48.48,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那就以新目的地为目标吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:53.36,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如果能坚信自己所喜欢的事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:58.44,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那就怀揣这份雀跃感前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:01.20,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}舍弃胆小的坏习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:03.78,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}用那份灿烂的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:06.12,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}飞翔  飞翔  朝着更高的目标
