Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.65,0:22:28.15,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}小小的愿望化为了明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:34.29,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只要大家期望  那就能够做到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:37.25,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}比谁都要努力
